        <h5>Golden tips to be an amazing adventurer</h5>
        <p>1. Plan your trip<br>
        2. You are responsible for your own safety<br>
        3. Be careful with the places you go<br>
        4. Bring your garbage back<br>
        5. Leave everything in its place<br>
        6. Take extreme care with fire<br>
        7. Honor the Animals and Plants<br>
        8. Be courteous to the local population and with other visitors<br>
        9. Buy locally produced items<br>
        10. Recycle and always try to reduce impacts</p>
        <br>
        <p>- WWF'S Sustainable Passport for Traveling with Balance</p>
      </div>
    </div>
